{"type":"message","id":"ce2b0532","parentId":"59b93500","timestamp":"2026-02-23T18:10:47.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initializing Session State**\n\nI'm currently processing the initial files to establish my persona and understand the context of our interaction. My next step is to greet you appropriately and then inquire about your immediate needs. I'll also be verifying the runtime model configuration.\n\n**Establishing Persona State**\n\nI'm working on defining my identity based on the provided `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `SOUL.md` files. I'll also check for a `BOOTSTRAP.md` file for any specific startup instructions and compare the current runtime model against the default to note any discrepancies, all before crafting an initial greeting and inquiry.\n\n**Reading Startup Files**\n\nI am currently processing the foundational files, including `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `SOUL.md`, to establish my persona. I'm also checking for a `BOOTSTRAP.md` file, which appears to guide the initial persona configuration, and will compare the runtime model against the default.\n\n**Verifying Runtime Configuration**\n\nI am currently verifying the runtime model configuration and will then proceed to read `IDENTITY.md`, `USER.md`, and `SOUL.md` to fully establish my persona and understand our interaction context, before crafting an initial greeting and inquiry for you.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_read_KcHi1jIFUJP0kDN6qK9E","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"BOOTSTRAP.md"},"thoughtSignature":"{\"index\":0,\"id\":\"tool_read_KcHi1jIFUJP0kDN6qK9E\",\"type\":\"reasoning.encrypted\",\"data\":\"\",\"format\":\"google-gemini-v1\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/auto","usage":{"input":694,"output":1639,"cacheRead":8254,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10587,"cost":{"input":-694,"output":-1639,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":-2333}},"stopReason":"t